    <para id="import-auto-id1165243121494">Magnetic Moment(μ) of Orbiting Electron is anti-parallel to Orbital Angular Momentum (L) as shown in Figure 7.22..</para>
    <para id="import-auto-id1165244676276">Similarly:</para>
    <figure id="import-auto-id1165242822515">
      <media id="import-auto-id1165243256048" alt="">
        <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics6-56b1.png" height="39" width="603"/>
      </media>
