    <para id="import-auto-id1165252902376">In a preferred direction say Z-direction we have the projection of L and S on Z-axis.</para>
    <para id="import-auto-id1165247336402">We have seen in Quantum Mechanics that :</para>
    <figure id="import-auto-id1165242749577">
      <media id="import-auto-id1165244574970" alt="">
        <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics7-4b4c.png" height="43" width="622"/>
